&lt;h3&gt;About the role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll join Flipdish’s Finance team, helping ensure our finance operations are accurate, controlled, scalable, and ready to support a growing multi-entity business. You’ll partner closely with Finance leadership and cross-functional stakeholders to own month-end close, strengthen controls, manage tax compliance, and support reporting requirements across the group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Success in this role looks like reliable month-end delivery, stronger financial processes, clear controls, and a well-supported finance team that can operate with pace and accuracy in a changing environment.&lt;/p&gt;
