&lt;li&gt;Bring strong technical accounting capability and confidence working across monthly accounts, consolidation preparation, audit, tax, and controls.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have proven experience leading, managing, or developing a small, high-performing finance team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have working knowledge of tax compliance, including coordinating filings, payments, and deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can show a track record of improving monthly financial processes and making finance operations more efficient.&lt;/li&gt;
