&lt;p&gt;You’ll thrive in this role if you:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have strong product design experience in a fast-paced, product-led environment (B2B SaaS experience is a plus).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can demonstrate proven ability to turn complex requirements into simple, intuitive experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have excellent visual craft and UX thinking, with a portfolio that shows shipped work and impact.&lt;/li&gt;
