&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Web Developer&lt;/strong&gt; to take ownership of &lt;a href=&quot;http://Flipdish.com&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flipdish.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;—our corporate website and a key brand asset. You’ll develop, maintain, and optimise the site to ensure it delivers a best-in-class user experience, performance, and scalability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Craft CMS&lt;/strong&gt; experience is highly desirable, along with a strong eye for design detail, clear communication, and comfort working in sprint cycles. You’ll partner closely with marketing, design, and other business stakeholders to ensure &lt;a href=&quot;http://Flipdish.com&quot;&gt;Flipdish.com&lt;/a&gt; consistently reflects our brand and supports our global growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&lt;/strong&gt; This role requires strong English communication skills (written and verbal), as English is our primary working language.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you’ll own&lt;/h3&gt;
