&lt;li&gt;Manage hosting and infrastructure needs, including server setup, Cloudflare, domains, SSL certificates, and backups.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and update landing pages using &lt;strong&gt;Twig templates&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;SCSS&lt;/strong&gt;, with high attention to design detail and brand consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
