&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with project managers, designers, and leadership to scope work clearly and deliver updates on time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run thorough QA and testing before deployments to reduce regressions and maintain quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Challenge poor decisions and propose better ways of working. Constructive challenge is a responsibility - prioritising harmony over truth or progress is a failure of responsibility.&lt;/li&gt;
